<li id="cite_note-Stax-10"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Stax_10-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span id="CITEREFStax2002" class="citation">Stax (April 4, 2002), <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://movies.ign.com/articles/356/356712p1.html"><i>The Stax Report's</i> Five Scribes <i>Edition</i></a>, IGN<span class="reference-accessdate">, retrieved <span class="nowrap">February 27,</span> 2009</span></span><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AGladiator+%282000+film%29&amp;rft.aulast=Stax&amp;rft.au=Stax&amp;rft.btitle=The+Stax+Report%27s+Five+Scribes+Edition&amp;rft.date=April+4%2C+2002&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fmovies.ign.com%2Farticles%2F356%2F356712p1.html&amp;rft.pub=IGN&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>
